    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >From one of the designers on <i>Murderhouse</i>!</h2>Consume Thy Flesh is a bite-sized physics based Halloween hootenanny! Players must roll their gargantuan gourd to blood-thirsty rug-rats below, so they may dine on your candy packed insides. Maintain momentum, catch some sick air, and splatter your insides all over. The ravenous spirits of Samhain must be satiated.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hello Boils and Ghouls, you're in for a treat!</h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unlock and explore 15 handcrafted levels!<br></li><li>Master your gourd physics, and hurl yourself over the moonlit rooftops of this spooky little town!<br></li><li>Splatter your candy filled insides inside the target zone of sugar crazed trick-r-treaters and collect candy corn coins for maximum points!<br></li><li>Help shut the door between the world of the living and the dead!</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802620/extras/aac23382dfc229e47e7c21e4ffb5603d.poster.avif?t=1749164113\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802620/extras/aac23382dfc229e47e7c21e4ffb5603d.webm?t=1749164113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802620/extras/aac23382dfc229e47e7c21e4ffb5603d.mp4?t=1749164113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802620/extras/984e55d459a6e3081457a42584f8d7dd.poster.avif?t=1749164113\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802620/extras/984e55d459a6e3081457a42584f8d7dd.webm?t=1749164113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https:/